**Privacy Policy for BMI Tracker**

This Privacy Policy outlines how personal information is collected, used, and disclosed by the BMI Tracker mobile application ("App").

**1. Information Collection and Use**

The BMI Tracker App calculates and provides Body Mass Index (BMI) values and corresponding BMI weight status categories for adults aged 20 and above. The App does not collect any personal information from its users. It solely utilizes locally stored data for the purpose of calculating and displaying BMI scores.

**2. Collection of Non-Personal Information**

The App may collect non-personal information automatically, including but not limited to device information, usage data, and diagnostic information. This information is collected to improve the performance and functionality of the App and is not linked to any identifiable user.

**3. Data Security**

We are committed to protecting the security of user information. The App employs industry-standard security measures to safeguard against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction of data.

**4. Third-Party Services**

The App may integrate third-party services such as analytics tools or advertisements. These services may collect non-personal information in accordance with their respective privacy policies. Users are encouraged to review the privacy policies of these third-party services.

**5. Children's Privacy**

The BMI Tracker App is not directed towards individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe that we have inadvertently collected personal information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately, and we will promptly take steps to remove such information.

**6. Changes to this Privacy Policy**

We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the revised Privacy Policy on this page.

**7. Contact Us**

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the privacy practices of the BMI Tracker App, don't hesitate to get in touch with us at zernoh@outlook.com.

By using the BMI Tracker App, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

Last updated: [02 April, 2024]

